  Welcome to PenTrix Linux CTF
  A vulnerable training machine with 10 hidden flags.
  
  Your mission: Find all 10 flags and root this box!
  
  Hints:
  • Start with web recon (port 80)
  • Check common files: robots.txt, page source
  • Enumerate users, permissions, cron jobs
  • Look for SUID binaries and Linux capabilities
  • Check /var/backups and /var/mail
  • Explore the network — you're not alone
  • Escalate privileges to root
